reviewText: I really really want this movie.  It's my favorite

This movie will teach you about love, life, living and legacy.
Julie Ellis and Luke Muldenhower are high schoolers in love. They had great prospects and life going
great. Luke is going to get a scholarship for football and Julie is an honors student. Suddenly, things went awry when Luke's health went bad.
Luke's mum fought hard but, Luke  died but left great legacies in his school and community that a stadium was named after him.

The movie educates and inspires me.
